{"tid":2044810,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"國際社群電競賽事 AEC 開放報名 !","createTime":"2020-05-31T10:46:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T10:46:14.000Z","uid":54789,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"043a6d2c823abd61d7e25c25d01ad7367511645a","tid":2044810,"uid":54789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xhx9AQN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXhx9AQN.jpg&h=4c3b03a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首個綜合性跨國際社群賽事<br />\n香港地區玩家亦能報名參與<br />\n臺灣最大業餘聯賽《亞洲電子競技公開賽》將於5/29開放報名<br />\n本次將設有《英雄聯盟》與《爐石戰記》兩個項目<br />\n總獎金高達250萬台幣<br />\n玩家首戰勝利即可獲獎<br />\n<br />\n續寫傳奇還是成為初茁新秀<br />\n《亞洲電子競技公開賽》成為征戰的第一站<br />\n<br />\n詳細資訊請上官網查詢：<a href=\"https://www.carry.live/2020AEC/index.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.carry.live%2F2020AEC%2Findex.php&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=347dc2ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.carry.live/2020AEC/index.php</a><br />\n組隊、約戰官方社團：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/CarryAEC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2FCarryAEC&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=c375938b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/CarryAEC</a>"}]}